						<p>On a pillar in the <hi rend="italic">mahamaṇḍapa</hi> of the Viṭṭhalēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>GAṆAPATI DHĀTU.</p>						

						<p>This is dated cyclic year Dhātu, Māgha, śu. This inscription can be assigned to the 13th century A.D. on the bassis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>Damaged and incomplete. Mentions Gaṇapati.</p>						

